        <section class="faq mt-4">
            <div class="question">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-11">
                            <h3 class="title">How can I register to the system?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1">
                            <span id="1"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <img class="img" src="~/media/profil.png" alt="" width="1250px" height="400px">
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-11">
                            <h3 class="title">I forgot my password, what should I do?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1">
                            <span id="2"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="p">Click on the "Forgot my Password" option on the login screen. You can receive a password reset link by entering your email address. You can create a new password through this link.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-11">
                            <h3 class="title">Which information should I use to log in?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1">
                            <span id="3"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="p">You should use the email address and password you used during registration. If you're having trouble logging in, you can try the "Forgot my Password" option.</p>
                <a href="~/media/"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-11">
                            <h3 class="title">How can I view the books?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1">
                            <span id="4"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="p">You can view all of our books by clicking on the "Book Search" tab in the main menu. You can quickly find the books you want using the search box or filtering options.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-11">
                            <h3 class="title">How can I see the details of a book?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1">
                            <span id="5"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="p">By clicking on a book in our catalog, you can reach the details page where you can see author information, description, stock status, and the book photo.</p>

            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-11">
                            <h3 class="title">How can I reserve a book?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1">
                            <span id="6"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="p">After logging in, go to the details page of the book you want and click the "Make a Reservation" button. Your request will be reviewed by the admin, and once approved, you will be notified.</p>

            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-11">
                            <h3 class="title">When will my reservation be ready?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1">
                            <span id="7"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="p">The admin will evaluate your request as soon as possible. You will receive a notification by email or within the system when your reservation is approved.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-11">
                            <h3 class="title">Can I cancel my reservation?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1">
                            <span id="8"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="p">Yes. You can go to the "My Reservations" section in your user panel, select the reservation you want to cancel, and click the "Cancel" button.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-11">
                            <h3 class="title">Is my information secure in the system?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1">
                            <span id="9"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="p">Yes, your information is securely stored. Your passwords are protected with strong encryption methods, and your personal data is not shared with third parties.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-11">
                            <h3 class="title">How can I update my information on my profile page?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1">
                            <span id="10"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="p">Go to your profile page and click the "Update My Information" button. Then, you can enter your new first name, last name, email address, etc., and update them. Click the "Save" button to complete the update.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="question">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-11">
                            <h3 class="title">Which browsers do you support?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-1">
                            <span id="11"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="p">Our system is fully compatible with popular browsers such as Chrome, Firefox, Edge, and Safari.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

        <!--FAQ section finished -->






